  <thing id="rauEWMaste" name="Earth and Water Mastery" description="A muck creature gains a +1 morale bonus on attack and damage rolls (already factored into his stats) as long as he touches earth or water (or a combination of both). It takes a -4 morale penalty on attack and damage rolls when attacking an airborne creature or attacking while airborne." compset="RaceSpec">
