  <thing id="rauDPNalSm" name="Smite" description="Three times per day, a nalfeshnee-possessed creature can cause a burst of unwholesome, multicolored light to explode from its body in a 60-foot radius. Every creature other than a demon in this area must succeed on a Will saving throw (DC 10 + 1/2 nalfeshnee-possessed creature&apos;s character level + nalfeshnee-possessed creature&apos;s Cha modifier) or be dazed for 1d10 rounds. The nalfeshnee-possessed creature is immune to this effect." compset="RaceSpec">
