  <thing id="rauBrmPkWh" name="Prickle Whip" description="Once per day, a bramble can unravel and detach one of the tangled strands that form its body. Doing so requires the same kind of action as drawing a melee weapon. This strand then functions as a whip sized for the bramble, except that the damage it deals is lethal and is not negated by armor or natural armor of any value. The whip becomes stiff, brittle, and useless after 1 hour." compset="RaceSpec">
