  <thing id="rauBrmThnD" name="Thorn Dart" description="Twice per day per character level, a bramble can pull a long thorn from its body. Doing so requires the same kind of action as drawing a dart. This thorn functions like a dart in all ways, and the bramble is automatically proficient with it." compset="RaceSpec">
