  <thing id="rauBrmThWk" name="Thorn Walk" description="This ability works like the tree stride spell (caster level equals bramble&apos;s character level), except that the bramble can travel only through trees that produce thorns or burrs. In addition, a bramble can move through a wall of thorns or any similar thorn-related eff ect without taking damage or suff ering any impairment. Thorn walk is usable once per day, plus one additional time per day for each 5 character levels the bramble possesses." compset="RaceSpec">
