  <thing id="rauJBStatF" name="Statue Form" description="At will and as a free action, a jotunblood troll may turn itself to stone as though with the statue spell, gaining a hardness of 8. It can remain in this form as long as it wishes. As with the spell, it can return to normal as a free action, act, and then become a statue again as a free action. This ability is likely the source of the erroneous belief that sunlight can turn a troll to stone." compset="RaceSpec">
