  <thing id="rauCBStunS" name="Stunning Strike" description="Five times per day as a free action, an astral-devablessed creature can imbue a single melee attack with stunning power. The player must declare the use of this ability before making the attack roll. A creature damaged by such an attack must succeed on a Fortitude saving throw (DC 10 + 1/2 celestial-blessed creature&apos;s character level + celestial-blessed creature&apos;s Con modifier) or be stunned for 1d6 rounds. If the attack misses or the astral-deva-blessed creature does not make the attack within 1 round of imbuing the melee weapon with power, that daily use of the ability is wasted" compset="RaceSpec">
