  <thing id="rauCysImmL" name="Immune to Light Effects" description="A crystal creature is immune to the harmful effects of bright light (including effects that blind with light); effects with the light descriptor; and other light-based attacks such as color spray, prismatic spray, and searing light. If the creature is hit with such an effect, the DC for its dazzling form attack increases by +2." compset="RaceSpec">
