  <thing id="rauCryBril" name="Brilliant Pestilence" description="The creature&apos;s natural attacks inflict a supernatural disease. \n\nBite or claw-injury; save Fort DC 23; onset 1 day; frequency 1 day; effect 1d6 Dex damage; cure 2 consecutive saves. \n\nA creature whose Dexterity is reduced to 0 by the disease is petrified and transformed into lifeless crystal. A creature with the earth subtype that is petrified by this disease revives 24 hours later and gains the crystal creature template. Once transformed, only miracle, polymorph any object, or wish restores the transformed earth creature." compset="RaceSpec">
