  <thing id="rauCryDazF" name="Dazzling Form" description="A crystalline creature refracts and reflects a dazzling cascade of light when illuminated. In normal light, this radiance extends 30 feet; in bright light, it extends 60 feet. Within this area, all sighted creatures are dazzled for 1 minute if they fail a Fortitude save (DC 10 + 1/2 the creature&apos;s racial Hit Dice + the creature&apos;s Charisma modifier). Creatures within this radius that are looking at the crystal xorn must save every round or become permanently blind (Fortitude negates); this is a gaze attack. The DC of these abilities increases by +2 in bright light." compset="RaceSpec">
