  <thing id="rauDBBattF" name="Battle Frenzy" description="Twice per day, a bearded devil-bound creature can work itself into a battle frenzy similar to a barbarian&apos;s rage (+4 Strength, +4 Constitution, +2 morale bonus on Will saves, –2 penalty to AC). This frenzy lasts for 3 rounds plus the bearded devil-bound creature&apos;s Con modifier (elevated for frenzy)." compset="RaceSpec">
