  <thing id="rauDvBInvL" name="Invisibile in Light" description="At will as a free action, a hellcat-bound creature can become invisible in any area that is lit well enough for a human to see. In a darkened area, it shows up as a faintly glowing outline visible up to 30 feet away (or 60 feet if the viewer has low-light vision). Magical darkness smothers the glow and conceals the outline." compset="RaceSpec">
