  <thing id="rauDvBFeaA" name="Fear Aura" description="At will, a devil-bound creature can radiate a fear aura as a free action. Every creature in the area must succeed on a Will save (DC 10 + 1/2 devil-bound creature&apos;s character level + devil-bound creature&apos;s Cha modifier) or be affected as though by a fear spell (caster level equals horned-devil-bound creature&apos;s character level). Devils are immune to this aura." compset="RaceSpec" summary="Foes within radius are affected by the {i}fear{/i} spell.">
