  <thing id="rauDWSDayV" name="Daylight Vulnerability" description="A dread wraith sovereign is not powerless in natural daylight and does not flee from it like a normal wraith does, but it does take a -4 penalty on all attack rolls, checks, and saves when in natural sunlight (but not within the radius of a daylight spell)." compset="RaceSpec">
