  <thing id="JBUADrdGha" name="Unnatural Aura" description="Animals, whether wild or domesticated, can sense the unnatural presence of a dread ghast at a distance of 30 feet. They do not willingly approach nearer than that and panic if forced to do so unless a master succeeds at a DC 25 Handle Animal, Ride, or wild empathy check. A panicked animal remains so as long as it is within 30 feet of the dread ghast." compset="RaceSpec">
