  <thing id="raABFearA" name="Fear Aura" description="Each creature within 100 feet of an apocalypse swarm that witnesses it bringing down another creature must succeed on a Will save (DC 10 + 1/2 apocalypse swarm&apos;s racial HD + apocalypse swarm&apos;s Cha modifier) or be frightened for 1 minute. Success leaves the creature shaken for 1 minute but does not negate the need to make a new saving throw for each such incident.  Fear is a mindaffecting fear effect." compset="RaceSpec" summary="Foes within radius are affected by the {i}fear{/i} spell.">
