  <thing id="raABPoiBld" name="Poisoned Blood" description="Ingested, Fortitude DC 10 + 1/2 blood knight&apos;s character level + blood knight&apos;s Cha modifier, initial damage 1d6 Con, secondary damage nausea for 1 minute.  Any opponent that strikes a blood knight with a bite attack is subject to this attack, as is any creature in the area of the fountain of blood attack." compset="RaceSpec">
