  <thing id="raABBrmGrb" name="Improved Grab" description="To use this ability, a bramble must hit with any one of its natural attacks. It can then attempt to start a grapple as a free action without provoking an attack of opportunity. If it wins the grapple check, it establishes a hold and can use its thorny grasp ability." compset="RaceSpec">
