  <thing id="raABCvSkil" name="Cave Skill Bonuses" description="A cave creature receives a +8 racial bonus on Climb checks and can always choose to take 10 on Climb checks, even if rushed or threatened.\n\n*Since cave creatures tend to be colored much like the caves in which they live, a cave creature in an area of natural stone gains a +4 circumstance bonus on Hide checks." compset="RaceSpec">
