  <thing id="raDMuCoUnd" name="Command Undead" description="As a free action, a dread mummy can automatically command all normal undead within 30 feet, except those with more character levels or higher Charisma scores than the dread mummy. Undead that fit these parameters never attack a dread mummy unless compelled." compset="RaceSpec" summary="Automatically command all normal undead within 30 feet.">
