  <thing id="raDMuGoDsp" name="Gaze of Despair" description="Any creature within 100 feet of a dread mummy that meets its gaze must succeed on a Fortitude save (DC 10 + 1/2 dread mummy&apos;s character level + dread mummy&apos;s Cha modifier) or be paralyzed for 1d4 rounds. Gaze of despair is a mind-affecting fear effect." compset="RaceSpec" summary="Gaze at creature within 100&apos; for paralysis 1d4 rounds." uniqueness="useronce">
