  <thing id="raUnAuraUn" name="Unnatural Aura (Undead)" description="Animals, whether wild or domesticated, can sense the unnatural presence of the undead at a distance of 30 feet. They do not willingly approach nearer than that and panic if forced to do so unless a master succeeds at a DC 25 Handle Animal, Ride, or wild empathy check. A panicked animal remains so as long as it is within 30 feet of the undead." compset="RaceSpec" summary="Animals do not willingly approach the undead." uniqueness="useronce">
